  "content": "\n \n \n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\">①项目：Qwen3-30B-A3B-Instruct-2507</span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"444\" data-imgfileid=\"100015419\" data-ratio=\"0.5495049504950495\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"808\" data-width=\"808\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=95bbcd01&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzFvuzibG5DuQTq17UlSEXdlvPBhuLav0VGjI6e48SOCicqXzguks62bEak30knnmZia5Qj6tvajMiaew%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.51px;text-align: start;\">★<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Qwen3-30B-A3B-Instruct-2507 是 Qwen3-30B-A3B 的更新版本，具有显著的通用能力提升，包括指令遵循、逻辑推理、文本理解、数学、科学、编码和工具使用等方面。</span>该模型在多语言的长尾知识覆盖上有显著提升，并在主观和开放性任务中更好地符合用户偏好，生成更高质量的文本。此外，该模型在256K长上下文理解方面也有增强。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/qwen3\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/qwen3</a></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\">②项目：Skywork-UniPic</span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"207\" data-imgfileid=\"100015416\" data-ratio=\"0.2571428571428571\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"805\" data-width=\"805\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1004ae86&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzFvuzibG5DuQTq17UlSEXdl9cccKo5iaW9CMypuBS5tRh3XASBnN2Y9lrwygtwAz1Fnt8ZEoHW8Kfg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.51px;text-align: start;\">★<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Skywork-UniPic 是一个拥有15亿参数的统一自回归多模态模型，能够在单一架构中处理三个关键的视觉语言任务：图像理解、文本到图像生成和图像编辑。</span>该模型从头开始在大规模多模态语料库上进行训练，旨在高效支持广泛的统一图像-文本任务。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/skywork-unipic\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/skywork-unipic</a></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\">③项目：Meta SecAlign</span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5117139334155364\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"811\" data-width=\"811\" data-height=\"415\" data-imgfileid=\"100015418\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1f70e0dc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzFvuzibG5DuQTq17UlSEXdlqKiaWfYXHWkbHuFBCKLNaoIMiargofvptbU1Cb6Iiam9NCDxibnO64N9zQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.51px;text-align: start;\">★<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Meta SecAlign 是一个开源的大语言模型，专注于防御提示注入攻击。</span>该项目提供了一个具有内置模型级防御的开源和开放权重的 LLM，能够实现商业级模型性能。通过改进的 SOTA SecAlign 防御方法，Meta SecAlign 在9个实用性基准和7个安全性基准上进行了评估，展示了其在未见下游任务中的安全性，包括工具调用和代理网络导航。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/meta-secalign\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/meta-secalign</a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🤖 Agent开发</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\">①项目：WebShaper</span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.38613861386138615\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"808\" data-width=\"808\" data-height=\"312\" data-imgfileid=\"100015417\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=424dbb4b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzFvuzibG5DuQTq17UlSEXdlVCCq6LHgCrwV4EGNOt6BrpufgjHWbTqYYwD4gI0U5gQd8oKVvMIU0A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.51px;text-align: start;\">★<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">WebShaper 是由阿里巴巴 NLP 团队在 Hugging Face 上发布的数据集，主要用于自然语言处理任务。</span>该数据集以 JSON 格式提供，包含多种文本模式，适合用于文本分析和处理。WebShaper 数据集的设计旨在支持多种 NLP 应用场景，帮助研究人员和开发者更好地进行模型训练和评估。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/webshaper\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/webshaper</a></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\">②项目：Eigent</span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2696078431372549\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"816\" data-width=\"816\" data-height=\"220\" data-imgfileid=\"100015415\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d223b23f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzFvuzibG5DuQTq17UlSEXdlDBG1e9FQkL1JWUjotCtcL4NYLxgm3uDIl6A25fY5IOZW6cK2YgFdvQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.51px;text-align: start;\">★<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Eigent是全球首个多智能体工作系统的桌面应用程序，旨在帮助用户构建、管理和部署自定义的AI工作系统，将复杂的工作流转化为自动化任务。</span>基于CAMEL-AI的开源项目，Eigent通过并行执行、定制化和隐私保护来提升生产力。该项目完全开源，支持本地部署，并集成了MCP工具，适合企业级应用。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/eigent\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/eigent</a></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\">③项目：AI Doc Gen</span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5555555555555556\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"810\" data-width=\"810\" data-height=\"450\" data-imgfileid=\"100015420\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f4bb45c9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzFvuzibG5DuQTq17UlSEXdljQZ3GU9QL5TyFLq9UX0nyLm42njmAKMyIwv03k1Cq9cnEqL1UPGMfg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.51px;text-align: start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">★AI Documentation Generator是一个由AI驱动的多智能体系统，能够自动分析代码库并生成全面的文档。</span>该系统支持GitLab集成、并行处理和多种大型语言模型（LLM），以提高代码理解和开发者入职的效率。通过多智能体架构，系统能够进行专门的代码分析并生成结构化文档。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ai-doc-gen\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ai-doc-gen</a></span></p>\n \n",
